PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,8,FMichelle O'Neill has claimed Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer treated those from the region
OL,10,Fas "second-class citizens".
OL,12,FShe said the outgoing Prime Minister
OL,13,F"refused to meet" with the Stormont
OL,14,FExecutive in recent years.
OL,16,FThe Executive has complained that the
OL,17,Fregion is not funded to need, and
OL,18,Fministers have been unable to agree a
OL,19,Fbudget.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@ZO]uD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FSpeaking to media at Parliament
OL,8,FBuildings on Monday, Ms O'Neill gave
OL,9,Fher view on Sir Keir's government from
OL,10,Fher role and interactions with Number
OL,11,F10.
OL,13,FShe said: "Throughout the course of
OL,14,Fthe last few years Keir Starmer has
OL,15,Frefused to meet with this Executive to
OL,16,Fdiscuss the very issues that are
OL,17,Fconcerning people here.
OL,26,@uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"He has refused to meet myself and the
OL,8,Fdeputy First Minister in terms of the
OL,9,Fcost-of-living crisis, so that's
OL,10,Fsomething I take away from my
OL,11,Fexperience working with him in his
OL,12,Ftime in office.
OL,14,F"Is that good enough?
OL,16,F"What does that say about the people
OL,17,Fhere?
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"It says that they're second-class
OL,8,Fcitizens and they'll never be up the
OL,9,Fpriority list of any British prime
OL,10,Fminister."
OL,12,FWhile Ms O'Neill said she is "ready to
OL,13,Fwork constructively" with the next
OL,14,Fprime minister, she also reiterated
OL,15,Fher view that the region's future is
OL,16,F"better served by breaking our links
OL,17,Fwith Britain".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]tD@^OUuD@TO]xD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson accused Sir
OL,8,FKeir of "leaving behind a record of
OL,9,Funfulfilled promises" in terms of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FHe said: "He failed to deal with the
OL,13,Froot cause of the problems created by
OL,14,Fthe (Northern Ireland) Protocol and
OL,15,FWindsor Framework, namely restoring
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's full place within
OL,17,Fthe United Kingdom and ending the
OL,18,Fapplication of EU laws over part of
OL,19,Four country.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@UO]tD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"His Government also failed to secure
OL,8,Four borders at a time of growing
OL,9,Fpublic concern about illegal migration.
OL,11,F"Whoever succeeds Sir Keir Starmer
OL,12,Fmust fund Northern Ireland properly,
OL,13,Fback those who work, restore
OL,14,Fconfidence in our borders, and deliver
OL,15,Fpolicies that strengthen the United
OL,16,FKingdom rather than weaken it."
OL,18,FAlliance leader Naomi Long expressed
OL,19,Fconcern about the potential for
OL,20,F"another period of instability" while
OL,21,Fthe next prime minister is agreed on.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@_O]|D@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FShe said: "My main concern is that
OL,8,Fthis gets resolved quickly, that we
OL,9,Fget some semblance of stability at
OL,10,FWestminster and that we're able to
OL,11,Fmake progress on the issues that
OL,12,Freally matter to the people we
OL,13,Frepresent, the cost-of-living crisis,
OL,14,Fbeing able to see opportunity for
OL,15,Ftheir families, dealing with all the
OL,16,Fchallenges in our health service and
OL,17,Fdealing with the financial challenges
OL,18,Fwe face as a devolved Assembly.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"We also need to see wider renewal of
OL,8,Fpolitics across the UK if people are
OL,9,Fgoing to be genuinely confident that
OL,10,FWestminster can deliver for them."
OL,12,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said Sir Keir
OL,13,Fhad been "more engaged and respectful
OL,14,Fof the island of Ireland and more
OL,15,Finterested in this region" than
OL,16,Fprevious premiers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]uD@JOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FShe said: "But he did fail to
OL,8,Fcommunicate and connect with his
OL,9,Felectorate, and some of it is about
OL,10,Fthe general structural challenges
OL,11,Ffacing the UK in terms of their
OL,12,Ffailure really to understand and have
OL,13,Fa shared story about how they are in
OL,14,Fthe world."
OL,16,FUUP leader Jon Burrows said Sir Keir
OL,17,Fhad been on "borrowed time".
OL,19,FHe said: "In 2024 the country voted
OL,20,Ffor change.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@KO]yD@MOUyD@[O]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"Instead, it got a government that too
OL,8,Foften failed to deliver.
OL,10,F"Taxes rose to record levels on
OL,11,Fworking families, while many of those
OL,12,Fwho do the right thing felt
OL,13,Fincreasingly overlooked.
OL,15,F"No matter who succeeds as prime
OL,16,Fminister, the Ulster Unionist Party
OL,17,Fwill work constructively with them
OL,18,Fbecause that is in the best interests
OL,19,Fof Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,F"But that relationship must work both
OL,8,Fways.
OL,10,F"The next government must govern for
OL,11,Fevery part of the United Kingdom,
OL,12,Fdeliver where this one failed, and
OL,13,Ftreat Northern Ireland as a full and
OL,14,Fequal partner in our Union."
OL,16,FTUV leader Jim Allister said the
OL,17,Fquestion for the next prime minister
OL,18,Fwill be whether they are a premier for
OL,19,Fthe whole United Kingdom, with
OL,20,Freference to the position of Northern
OL,21,FIreland following Brexit.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FThe region effectively continues to
OL,8,Ffollow some European Union rules under
OL,9,Fthe Windsor Framework accord in order
OL,10,Fto avoid a hard land border on the
OL,11,Fisland of Ireland.
OL,13,FMr Allister claimed Sir Keir "ran away
OL,14,Ffrom" the issue, but said
OL,15,F"constitutionally it has to be
OL,16,Faddressed".
OL,26,@uD@^OUvD@EO]wD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
