OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782317939
OL,3,CStarmer 'treated those from Northern
OL,4,CIreland as second-class citizens' `
OL,5,CO'Neill
OL,7,FHe added: "We're in a situation where
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, in those 300 areas
OL,9,Fof law, we're governed not by laws we
OL,10,Fmake here but by a foreign power, and
OL,11,Fif you're Prime Minister of the United
OL,12,FKingdom then your first duty is to
OL,13,Fensure that you exercise sovereignty
OL,14,Fover all of the United Kingdom."
